OL,7,FTata Steel has announced the coke
OL,8,Fovens at Port Talbot steelworks will
OL,9,Fclose on Wednesday, affecting around
OL,10,F200 jobs.
OL,12,FThe steelmaking giant has already
OL,13,Fannounced plans to cut around 3,000
OL,14,Fjobs from the site in an effort to
OL,15,Fdecarbonise the plant.
OL,17,FThe boss of has previously said he is
OL,18,F"100% committed to building an
OL,19,Felectric arc" at the .
