OL,5,Caffected
OL,7,Fsays it will cease operations at its
OL,8,F-based Morfa coke ovens from
OL,9,FWednesday, 20 March.
OL,11,FThis is due to what it describes as
OL,12,F"significantly deteriorating
OL,13,Foperational stability" but one union
OL,14,Fhas described the closure as a
OL,15,F"massive blow".
OL,17,FThe ovens are used to heat coal to
OL,18,Fcreate a hard residue called coke
OL,19,Fwhich is then used to fuel blast
OL,20,Ffurnaces.
