OL,5,Caffected
OL,7,FIt is understood that there will be no
OL,8,Fimmediate redundancies and Tata is
OL,9,Fexpecting to redeploy staff elsewhere
OL,10,Fin the business.
OL,12,FOnce the ovens are shut, Tata will
OL,13,Fhave to buy in all the coke it needs
OL,14,Ffor the steelmaking process.
OL,16,FSteel unions said they had been aware
OL,17,Fof concerns about the condition of the
OL,18,Fcoke ovens for some time, and
OL,19,Fpreviously said they would not oppose
OL,20,Fan early closure on safety grounds.
