OL,7,FCEO Rajesh Nair said: "We regret to
OL,8,Fannounce that we have been forced to
OL,9,Fmake the decision to cease operations
OL,10,Fat Morfa Coke Ovens from Wednesday 20
OL,11,FMarch as a result of significantly
OL,12,Fdeteriorating operational stability.
OL,14,F"In our recent discussions with our
OL,15,Ftrades union colleagues, the need to
OL,16,Fcease operations at the Morfa coke
OL,17,Fovens and one of the two blast
OL,18,Ffurnaces this summer is understood.
