OL,3,CTata Steel announces closure of Port
OL,4,CTalbot coke ovens as 200 workers
OL,5,Caffected
OL,7,F"The performance of the coke ovens has
OL,8,Fbeen deteriorating over many months,
OL,9,Fdespite some herculean efforts by the
OL,10,Fteams there. The condition of the
OL,11,Fovens has now worsened to a level
OL,12,Fmaking continued operation untenable.
OL,14,F"We will now begin the process of
OL,15,Fsafely closing and purging the coke
OL,16,Fovens, and ceasing operations at the
OL,17,Fadjoining By-Products plant.
