OL,10,Falignment with our ongoing wider
OL,11,Fconsultation programme.
OL,13,F"I'd like to give my sincere thanks
OL,14,Fand appreciation to all those who have
OL,15,Fworked at the Morfa coke ovens since
OL,16,Fits commissioning in 1981 ` I have
OL,17,Falways been struck by the spirit and
OL,18,Fcamaraderie of the workforce there who
OL,19,Fhave always given everything to the
OL,20,Fplant, often in very difficult
OL,21,Fcircumstances.
