OL,7,F"As part of our efforts to stem our
OL,8,Fcurrent losses, and given the
OL,9,Fcondition of the assets, we propose to
OL,10,Fclose the heavy end iron and
OL,11,Fsteelmaking assets at within this
OL,12,Fcalendar year in a phased manner.
OL,14,F" is investing #1.25billion investment
OL,15,Fin electric arc furnace-based capacity
OL,16,Fwhich will secure steel making in for
OL,17,Fthe long term `and facilitate a
OL,18,Ftransition to low-CO2 steelmaking.
